title: Mixtape Game: We Have a Twist This Week
description: Mixtape Game is different this week thanks to an idea from listener Bailey!  Dave, Jenny, and Tina have 3 random songs chosen but have no idea what the scenarios are yet.  Falen reads the scenarios and they try to sell why their random song works for it!
